00:13:21.660 --> 00:13:25.230
And so, you know he learned
the music and the arts,

00:13:25.230 --> 00:13:27.860
and he really wanted
to teach it.

00:13:27.860 --> 00:13:31.730
And teach the philosophy of
the great teacher to outsiders.

00:13:31.730 --> 00:13:35.510
That was, you know he really
