00:13:35.510 --> 00:14:05.040
[ Speaking in Foreign Language ]

00:14:05.040 --> 00:14:07.270
So, you know he really
wanted to teach outsiders,

00:14:07.270 --> 00:14:09.940
but at that point,
they were forbidden

00:14:09.940 --> 00:14:11.510
