00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:32.510
So, that it would someday be
presented on the world stage.

00:14:32.510 --> 00:15:16.040
[ Speaking in Foreign Language ]

00:15:16.040 --> 00:15:20.560
So, you know, he said
basically, so when I went there,

00:15:20.560 --> 00:15:21.860
I first went to the
[foreign word],

