this through out artform.

00:31:55.460 --> 00:32:01.960
So, it was in 2008 when
we first visit in Paris,

00:32:01.960 --> 00:32:06.980
the times we had first
to visit the textile.

00:32:06.980 --> 00:32:15.620
So, the net year 2009, that's
when I visit again in Paris

00:32:15.620 --> 00:32:19.100
at that time some ideas come

00:32:19.100 --> 00:32:25.330
